            <body style="background-color:sandybrown">
                <div class="jumbotron">
                    <h1>IotShop</h1>
                    <h2>Welcome to IotShop</h2>
                    <p>This is a Prototype that  has be created for the Honours Project Module</p>
                    <br />
                    <h3>How The Impact of RFID can Help Inventory control and also increase Productivity in companies</h3>

                </div>
