                    <div class="col-md-6  col-md-sm-4">
                        <h2>About  IotShop</h2>
                        <p>
                            Iot-Shop has been designed to use RFID sensor and Ultra Sonic range sensor to collect data.
                            This Program has been designed to help companies productivity levels, while using these Sensors.
                        </p>
                        <br />
                        <p>
                            Iot-Shop has been created using a number of frameworks, Programming languages
                            and also a Architecture Style.

                            Iot-Shops Front End is connected to a Arduino C++ Project, A data Class libary, local Database
                            And also An API.

                            The way that the program works is that it  uses the Arduino project code to connect to the Sensors
                            then storing and view the data that the sensors have read/outputed to the programs UI.

